summary: This document appears to be a log of background checks performed on individuals from the Ghislaine Maxwell trial witness list. It records the results of checks (positive or negative) against the EJustice system, with some entries noting expired protection orders. The document is heavily redacted, with no witness names visible.

events.title: Witness List Background Checks
events.description: Background checks were performed on individuals from the Ghislaine Maxwell trial witness list using the EJustice system. Results were recorded as 'Positive' or 'Negative', with some positive hits noting an expired protection order.

keyFacts: The document is a log of background checks on the Ghislaine Maxwell trial witness list conducted on October 5-6, 2021.
All witness names are fully redacted in the provided text, indicated by 'I I I' placeholders.
Checks were run against the 'EJustice' system, with results recorded as 'Positive' or 'Negative'.
Some positive results indicated an 'expired protection order' for at least one individual.
The document is part of a series, as indicated by file references EFTA00068960 through EFTA00068963.
